<h2>Dashboard: Admin Panel <i>IIIT KOTA</i></h2>
<p>Role: </p>
<p>Ip: {{this.ip}}</p>
<br /><br />
<h3>Generate cloud link:</h3>
<p>If your action requires images first generate their urls here.</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-4 col-lg-3 crd">
    Generate cloud stored link
    <form id="upload-form" action="/upload?token={{this.token}}" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <h3>Select an image to upload:</h3>
      <div class="upload-container"><input id="file-picker" type="file" name="image"></div>
      <div><input class="btn btn-warning" type="submit" value="Upload Image"></div>
    </form>
  </div>
  {{!-- <div class="col-lg-2">
  </div> --}}
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-6">
    <div style="height:240px;width:100%;border:1px solid #F4A460;font:16px/26px Georgia, Garamond, Serif;overflow:auto;padding:20px;">
    <p>Links generated so far</p>
    <ol>
      {{#each this.resources1}}
          <li>https://{{../accountName}}.blob.core.windows.net/{{../containerName}}/{{name}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<br />
<h3>Add new or Remove existing faculties here</h3>
<p>Please note that, your activites will be recorded</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h4>Add New Faculty👨‍🏫</h4>
    <h3>Click the button to proceed</h3>
    <p>This feature is only for admins, not coadmins</p>
    <a href="/add/faculty?token={{this.token}}" style="text-decoration: none;"><button id="addfaculty" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Add</button></a>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6  col-lg-3 crd">
    <h4>Remove Faculty👩‍🏫</h4>
    <h3>Click the button to proceed</h3>
    <p>This feature is only for admins, not coadmins</p>
    <a href="/remove/faculty?token={{this.token}}" style="text-decoration: none;"><button id="removefaculty" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Remove</button></a>
 
  </div>
</div>
<br /><br />
<h3>Create Notice/News/Article here..</h3>
<p>Please note that, your activites will be recorded</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-4 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h3>Add New Notice📑</h3>
    <p>Rememeber once added you <strong>cannot</strong> delete it.</p>
    <button id="addnotice" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Add</button>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-4 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h3>Add News 📰</h3>
    <p>Rememeber once added you <strong>cannot</strong> delete it.</p>
    <button id="addnews" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Add</button>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-4 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h3>Add New Article 📕</h3>
    <p>Rememeber once added you <strong>cannot</strong> delete it.</p>
    <button id="addarticle" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Add</button>
  </div>
</div>
<br /><br />
<h3>Create News event here</h3>
<p>Please note that, event according to their planned dates will automatically be shifted to upcoming or past events
  sections.</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h3>Add Event🎫</h3>
    <p>You can delete an event anytime.</p>
    <button id="addevent" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Add</button>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-3 crd">
    <h3>Delete Event🎟️</h3>
    <p>You can delete any event.</p>
    <button id="addevent" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning">Delete</button>
  </div>

</div>

